{"tid":2312871,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《大公報》經濟部員工確診 同部門人員WFH","createTime":"2020-12-05T10:38:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T07:24:13.000Z","uid":5195,"like":64,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"3441f5311a2083fab32e5e57205eed57cf5f3948","tid":2312871,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T10:38:02.000Z","msg":"，《大公報》編輯部今日中午向員工發出通知，指因經濟部有同事確診，經濟部全體人員即時啟動居家辦公模式，待檢測出結果確認安全後才返辦公室。該報並指示29樓全體人員盡快檢測，240元檢測費可交行政報銷。29樓辦公場地已安排徹底清潔消毒。<br />\n<br />\n另外，已與《大公報》合併的《文匯報》，有員工今日也收到公司發出的短訊，相信因為《文匯報》與《大公報》的辦公室是同一幢樓宇內。該短訊指「今日又有行家確診」，提醒同事嚴守防疫禁令，認真執行居家辦公安排，盡快不要參加社交活動，記者完成採訪在家寫稿等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201205/VLSOJFCSJZGL3GCGDYAA7HV2O4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201205%2FVLSOJFCSJZGL3GCGDYAA7HV2O4%2F&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1wzQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=a4063651\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201205%2FVLSOJFCSJZGL3GCGDYAA7HV2O4%2F&h=66d79199\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201205/VLSOJFCSJZGL3GCGDYAA7HV2O4/</a>"},{"pid":"ca58f733158edebb5d58fa4716d6024eaec47a28","tid":2312871,"uid":284855,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T10:39:11.000Z","msg":"乜唔係WTF<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7e3a5d6d2a8451724ec3ca9f847b74f6fa5df5","tid":2312871,"uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T10:39:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"385aa8b55ddb6d40f6f67f72a44f7b82f0896175","tid":23128